{"tid":1864090,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你，睇 清 呢 個 政 府 未 ？","createTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T17:36:04.000Z","uid":8794,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ac957651d7e2ef54bb24484dadae34594efecfa5","tid":1864090,"uid":8794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"不分藍黃 只講民生<br />\n<br />\n反送中事件你要聽中央話 無話事權 ok<br />\n<br />\n但係一直以來既樓價<br />\n<br />\n到宜家全城瘋搶物資 黑心藥房惡意抬價 <br />\n<br />\n一眾搶購衛生用品囤積再以高價網上發售既仆街<br />\n<br />\n發生咁多影響民生既事 點解政府都可以冇作為<br />\n<br />\n就算好多人憎既大陸 各省各城都陸續立法禁止商戶抬價/售賣偽劣衛生用品<br />\n<br />\n你呢個政府就完全冇理過所有事 連封關都係罷工逼出黎<br />\n<br />\n你班高級公務員知唔知連藍到黑既同事家人朋友都日日屌你地<br />\n<br />\n直到呢刻發現，原來我地一直生活係半癱瘓狀態政府既管治"},{"pid":"50930ea45776084ca5398bb92d47f67e7f7af5fe","tid":1864090,"uid":305009,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:51.000Z","msg":"到呢刻發現不如再遲啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf1fb504120730355375b33ebbb43a5185bcc69","tid":1864090,"uid":116938,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"未，屋企仲有人避講政府，仲有人話你知無睇新聞，唔知疫情唔知政府做過咩"},{"pid":"da5c9d13bcca0d687603e61e92ab0685fadc5c3c","tid":1864090,"uid":8794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50930ea45776084ca5398bb92d47f67e7f7af5fe","tid":1864090,"uid":305009,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:19:51.000Z","msg":"到呢刻發現不如再遲啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"提醒佢哋"},{"pid":"c4ae352625ba3ca31d3a12fb348209ff6208721c","tid":1864090,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:28:45.000Z","msg":"移民<br />\n順民<br />\n兩揀一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d11af629499bed08ff5c2de21b40470d3521f8","tid":1864090,"uid":153773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac957651d7e2ef54bb24484da